    "created_at": "2017-01-20T06:19:36Z",
    "updated_at": "2017-01-20T06:20:06Z",
    "body": "Just a heads up that I believe this is going to have a large impact\r\n\r\nBecause folks at 125% will finally get properly scaled content, everything will appear to be much larger for them.  If those people are upset and don't like this, it can be worked around by passing two additional flags to the base::CommandLine class (you should be able to append via the command line):\r\n`--high-dpi-support=1 --force-device-scale-factor=1`"
